57
00:04:37,050 --> 00:04:40,050
 grow your power in that seat. 

58
00:04:40,050 --> 00:04:43,350
 That's how you can protect yourself and your people. 

59
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:46,100
So, from the beginning, you knew...

60
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:52,000
You were the one who had people follow me in the U.S. and had those pictures exposed, Grandfather?

61
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,440
I-It's not true. Right?

62
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:57,020
