76
00:05:45,770 --> 00:05:49,960
If you tell the world what kind of a person you really are,

77
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:54,050
did you think those two would be at peace?

78
00:05:54,050 --> 00:05:56,720
Are you sure it's not just to put yourself at ease?

79
00:05:58,150 --> 00:06:00,020
- That's— 
 - Yes, that's...

80
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:04,560
you making a selfish decision again and using those two as an excuse.

81
00:06:05,450 --> 00:06:07,900
You're running away again.

82
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:13,770
Chairman.

83
00:06:13,770 --> 00:06:16,120
Right now, Ji Han is...

84
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,440
Ji Han!

85
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:31,340
Lee Ji Han!

86
00:06:35,530 --> 00:06:37,410
A Jeong.

87
00:06:46,500 --> 00:06:49,380
It's making me angry now.

88
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:52,170
