89
00:06:52,170 --> 00:06:56,350
He told me not to cry and made me stop crying like this.

90
00:06:57,190 --> 00:07:00,500
He told me to laugh, and this is how he makes me laugh.

91
00:07:03,650 --> 00:07:08,970
Your brother really has an innovative thought process.

92
00:07:08,970 --> 00:07:11,560
