109
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,790
A Jeong.

110
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:34,180
Sorry.

111
00:08:37,750 --> 00:08:41,400
Let me know when Lee Ji Han contacts you.

112
00:09:00,190 --> 00:09:03,180
What on earth is happening?

113
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:11,380
Honey,

114
00:09:11,380 --> 00:09:13,470
I think I really went back to that day.

115
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:16,300
The day we came to greet the parents and confessed about getting pregnant.

116
00:09:16,300 --> 00:09:19,920
Look! Even my body reacted.

117
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:23,470
Wow, my back and my guts both hurt.

118
00:09:25,530 --> 00:09:28,030
Shouldn't we just tell them honestly?

119
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:30,450
That A Jeong's marriage was fake.

120
00:09:30,450 --> 00:09:33,290
- And then? 
 - Still, we can tell them—

121
00:09:33,290 --> 00:09:36,820
That can clear the misunderstanding about her cheating.

122
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:41,060
Just keep your mouth shut, and don't make things worse.

123
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:43,410
Sis will take care of—

124
00:09:44,330 --> 00:09:47,590
- But she doesn't take care of things, though! 
 - Exactly!

125
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:51,230
It seemed like she didn't even know about the press conference.

126
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:55,350
Gosh, Na A Jeong! Seriously.

127
00:09:55,350 --> 00:09:56,960
What's this?

128
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:59,560
- Sis is back. 
 - Okay.

129
00:10:00,770 --> 00:10:04,120
What happened? And what's with the press conference, huh?

130
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,660
- A Jeong! 
 - Sis!

131
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:08,900
- A Jeong. 
 - Gosh, that's enough already.

132
00:10:08,900 --> 00:10:11,850
He was that kind of punk, to begin with.

133
00:10:11,850 --> 00:10:16,760
If he was in the wrong, he deserves to meet the consequences on his own. Right?

134
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:18,650
How dare he drag you into it?

135
00:10:18,650 --> 00:10:20,180
Mom,

136
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:23,600
I told you he's not like that.

137
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:26,210
Are you going to keep defending him like that?

138
00:10:26,210 --> 00:10:27,980
