139
00:10:27,980 --> 00:10:29,270
- What? 
 - Sis—

140
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:31,450
It was all a lie.

141
00:10:31,450 --> 00:10:33,770
It was all an act.

142
00:10:34,570 --> 00:10:36,920
I fooled all of you.

143
00:10:38,700 --> 00:10:41,050
What are you saying right now?

144
00:10:41,050 --> 00:10:46,160
I agreed to disguise marrying him because Do Han had a situation.

145
00:10:46,160 --> 00:10:49,300
He said he'd wrap things up nicely after three years.

146
00:10:49,300 --> 00:10:51,800
- And he'll give me money, too. 
 - That's enough.

147
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:54,450
But he said I'm the only one for the role.

148
00:10:54,450 --> 00:10:57,190
I guess I wanted to do something like this...

149
00:10:57,990 --> 00:11:00,460
for once in my life.

150
00:11:00,460 --> 00:11:03,220
Instead of supporting roles and extras I do every day,

151
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:06,290
I guess I wanted to take a role like this one for once.

152
00:11:07,090 --> 00:11:09,450
That's why things ended up this way.

153
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:12,900
They were all my choices.

154
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:18,750
But he's doing that to take all the blame alone.

155
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:23,460
It's my fault for lying to you, Mom and Dad...

156
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:29,900
But he's the person I like.

157
00:11:31,110 --> 00:11:33,240
He grew on me.

158
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:36,540
I can't live without him anymore,

159
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:40,840
but I don't even know where he is right now.

160
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:46,210
What am I supposed to do at times like this?

161
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:53,570
What am I supposed to do?

162
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:56,220
What took you so long?

163
00:12:58,990 --> 00:13:00,970
Why did you do that?

164
00:13:03,770 --> 00:13:06,040
Because it's the right thing.

165
00:13:08,690 --> 00:13:11,130
You answer too easily.

166
00:13:11,130 --> 00:13:13,690
I know it was hard to come to that decision.

167
00:13:13,690 --> 00:13:15,370
Brother,

168
00:13:16,930 --> 00:13:18,030
I'm really okay.

169
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:21,020
How can you possibly be okay?

170
00:13:21,020 --> 00:13:22,660
- Because of me, people are— 
 - This is why I came.

171
00:13:22,660 --> 00:13:24,860
- Because of me, people are— 
 - This is why I came.

172
00:13:25,980 --> 00:13:28,200
I was worried you'd think this way.

173
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:31,660
I'm sorry for making you shoulder

174
00:13:31,660 --> 00:13:36,680
unnecessary burden all this time, saying it was for your good.

175
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:38,780
However,

176
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:41,580
I quit doing things for your sake...

177
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:45,880
when I didn't want to.

178
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:49,340
I told you back then.

179
00:13:49,340 --> 00:13:53,970
Let's go our own ways and live happily now.

180
00:13:53,970 --> 00:13:56,840
I only made my choice.

181
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:06,370
Sorry.

182
00:14:07,770 --> 00:14:10,370
I'm really sorry.

183
00:14:10,370 --> 00:14:12,420
Do I need to repeat myself again?

184
00:14:12,420 --> 00:14:13,900
I don't have time for that.

185
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:18,020
Also, do you think I only came for you?

186
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:20,630
How's A Jeong?

187
00:14:20,630 --> 00:14:23,150
Go see her for yourself.

188
00:14:23,150 --> 00:14:25,590
I don't want to get beat up.

189
00:14:27,150 --> 00:14:31,070
She was having a really hard time.

190
00:14:32,380 --> 00:14:34,430
As expected.

191
00:14:36,230 --> 00:14:38,630
I couldn't bear to see that.

192
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:44,370
Please be by her side for a while in my place.

193
00:14:44,370 --> 00:14:47,430
- What about you? 
 - Don't tell her you met me.

194
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:51,030
I want her to...

195
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:55,580
forget me as soon as possible.

196
00:14:58,820 --> 00:15:00,540
I'll go now.

197
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:25,540
Yes, Father.

198
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:30,810
Of course, I'm already meeting the board members who are on Grandfather's side.

199
00:15:30,810 --> 00:15:33,370
It seems they're not quite happy right now.

200
00:15:33,370 --> 00:15:36,370
They seemed actually thankful we reached out to them first.

201
00:15:36,370 --> 00:15:39,860
 Still, don't let your guard down until the board meeting. 

202
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:45,910
 From what I hear, the board seems concerned about doing business with Taeyang. 

203
00:15:45,910 --> 00:15:47,770
Of course.

204
00:15:47,770 --> 00:15:50,170
I already told you.

205
00:15:50,170 --> 00:15:53,880
Taeyang won't just sit by and watch.

206
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:57,610
It's not like we didn't expect it. We just need to take our time and prepare.

207
00:15:57,610 --> 00:16:02,000
 All right. It seems you've got things under control, so I won't worry too much. 

208
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:07,200
Also, Father, even if this were to go wrong,

209
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:10,640
