210
00:16:11,830 --> 00:16:13,540
Yes.

211
00:16:35,790 --> 00:16:39,210
I can't believe he still kept that day's recording.

212
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:44,640
What on earth are you hiding, Grandfather?

213
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:04,540
You really don't know where Lee Ji Han is?

214
00:17:04,540 --> 00:17:08,190
I'm not hiding it. I couldn't find him anywhere in the country.

215
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:11,780
I said the same thing back when A Jeong was here, too.

216
00:17:13,230 --> 00:17:16,280
Jong Hee, is it still not done?

217
00:17:16,280 --> 00:17:19,090
I just need to put some fruit.

218
00:17:19,090 --> 00:17:22,700
Ji Ae, I feel very threatened right now,

219
00:17:22,700 --> 00:17:24,600
but I'm your other half.

220
00:17:24,600 --> 00:17:26,620
And A Jeong is my friend.

221
00:17:26,620 --> 00:17:28,600
I really don't know.

222
00:17:28,600 --> 00:17:30,320
You have no idea?

223
00:17:30,320 --> 00:17:34,660
A Jeong is in a terrible state, trying to find that man right now!

224
00:17:34,660 --> 00:17:37,780
I mean, I don't...

225
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:40,480
I don't think we'll get an answer, Unni.

226
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:42,080
- Let's go see A Jeong. 
 - Okay.

227
00:17:42,080 --> 00:17:43,490
You packed all the food, right?

228
00:17:43,490 --> 00:17:48,720
Yes, I packed porridge, soup, stew, fruits, large intestine, and chicken feet.

229
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:50,810
Everything that's easy on your stomach.

230
00:17:53,610 --> 00:17:56,160
Eun Taek, I'll let you go today.

231
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:59,400
But not a chance next time.

232
00:17:59,400 --> 00:18:03,900
I hope you find out where Lee Ji Han is quickly.

233
00:18:03,900 --> 00:18:06,200
And keep an eye on the store.

234
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:13,690
Gosh, where the heck is Ji Han, and what's he doing?

235
00:18:13,690 --> 00:18:16,010
Gosh, I'm worried!

