00:18:57,960 --> 00:19:03,910
♫  It was so nice when we shared those heartwarming words  ♫

237
00:19:03,910 --> 00:19:08,700
♫  Back then, we gave and received love  ♫

238
00:19:08,700 --> 00:19:11,910
The sun's still up?

239
00:19:11,910 --> 00:19:13,250
The time is passing so slowly.

240
00:19:21,990 --> 00:19:27,270
♫  I'll carefully share it all  ♫

241
00:19:28,120 --> 00:19:33,830
♫  So we don't get hurt anymore  ♫

242
00:19:33,830 --> 00:19:39,970
♫  The place where the well-rounded you and I will meet  ♫

243
00:19:39,970 --> 00:19:41,450
 Come back when I'm telling you nicely. 

244
00:19:41,450 --> 00:19:46,100
 Or else. I won't let you get away with this. 

245
00:19:46,100 --> 00:19:50,520
 It can't be. Right? We're not really finished like this. Right? 

246
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:53,540
 You went away briefly. Right? You'll come back. Right? 

247
00:19:53,540 --> 00:19:59,700
♫  It was great, we were smiling all the time  ♫

248
00:19:59,700 --> 00:20:08,340
♫  You said you'll tell me all the things you love in a small voice  ♫

249
00:20:08,340 --> 00:20:12,210
♫  You said we'll be together forever  ♫

250
00:20:16,300 --> 00:20:17,840
Mr. Driver, one moment.

251
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:22,700
♫  I'll carefully share it all  ♫

252
00:20:23,600 --> 00:20:29,290
♫  So we don't get hurt anymore  ♫

253
00:20:29,290 --> 00:20:35,290
♫  The place where the well-rounded you and I will meet  ♫

254
00:20:35,290 --> 00:20:43,150
♫  I love this place, and I'm sure you're the same  ♫

255
00:20:43,150 --> 00:20:48,820
♫  How can you be so much like this?  ♫

256
00:20:48,820 --> 00:20:53,440
 I went to your house again today. 

257
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:57,620
 Just when will you come? 

258
00:20:57,620 --> 00:21:00,670
 If you won't come, I'll go. 

259
00:21:00,670 --> 00:21:03,900
 I take back saying you can't get away with this. 

